data.description: This inviting 3 bedroom, 2 bath home located in Oak Point, Texas in Crescent Oak Beach Estates where you will have exclusive access to a private boat ramp and fishing dock on Lake Lewisville! Enjoy the tranquility on the oversized lot close to the lake but also only a few minutes from DFW Airport, all major highways as well as several options for shopping and entertainment. The 1260 sq.ft home features white diamond quartz kitchen countertops, subway tile backsplash, stainless steel farmhouse sink with pulldown sprayer faucet, beautiful decorative tile in kitchen and baths, durable vinyl plank flooring, soft close drawers throughout, stylish barn door into primary bed-bath, new stainless steel dishwasher! Step outside and enjoy the patio and huge backyard or take a short walk to the community pool or park. Whether you're an angler at heart, a watersports enthusiast or just looking for a nice place near the lake in a great community, this one's for you!
